### 1. create tenant (admin credential only)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8090/platform/v1/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv YUJIAN_PLATFORM_ADMIN_CREDENTIAL}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: onboarding-tenant-001

{"displayName":"演示租户","dataResidencyPolicy":"cn-mainland","planId":"plan-preview"}

### 2. issue a scoped room token
POST http://127.0.0.1:8090/platform/v1/rtc/token
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv YUJIAN_PLATFORM_CREDENTIAL}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"tenantId":"tenant-demo","projectId":"project-demo","environmentId":"environment-dev","roomName":"quickstart","participantIdentity":"console-user"}
